item.title: Introduction to discord.py (2)
item.description: #Introduction We run an unofficial server for discord.py (although some developers). Questions are also accepted here. If you would like to receive individual support, please enter from the invitation url below and DM to @@Smidora #8931`. https://discord.gg/KPp2Wsu **Please send any questions regarding this article here** About this article This article is a step-by-step article about discord.

item.title: PyTorch super introduction PyTorch basics
item.description: #Introduction This series is described as a summary of learning of PyTorch which is a machine learning framework of Python. This time, I have written a summary of the basics of PyTorch. It may be difficult to read as a reading material because I try to write down the main points rather than to convey it, but I hope you can use it to understand the points. What is #PyTorch As I mentioned earlier, PyTorch is a Python machine learning framework.
